description:
The Rock has met the biggest fight of his life, so in order to beat a standing petunia, the only attack he has is to spit some bars.

I am going to start re-uploading some videos from my Twitter onto YouTube
https://twitter.com/DitzyFlama/status/1484633940841295873?s=20

You can view the full version here!
https://soundcloud.com/ditzyflama/floweys-face-off

Credits 
Thank you @JeffSwiper for helping me rotoscope half of the video!
https://twitter.com/JeffSwiper
https://www.youtube.com/c/JeffSwiper

For the last remaining seconds of the video, I did everything from the sculpting, texturing, rigging and 3D animation!
